    public class ORMRelationGraphicalNodeEditPolicy
extends org.eclipse.gef.editpolicies.GraphicalNodeEditPolicy
    This GraphicalNodeEditPolicy handles request for the creations of all kinds of Relations between other Relations and creates and returns the necessary commands for that purpose. NewObject = O/o SourceEditPart = S/s TargetEditPart = T/t Model = M/m
    Author:
    Kay Bierzynski
